 At Grand Performance, to us service means both keeping your bike in great shape and providing answers to any questions you may have about it.  We have many years of hands-on experience with the best products in the bike industry and the knowledge gained from miles in the saddle and feedback from our racing teams/clubs.

Below is just a short list of common labor rates.

Tune Up 75
Tune Up +        95
Check Over 35
Flat Fix   8
Wheel True 25
Der/Br. adjust  15

Hourly rate       75

Please don't hesitate to stop in or call to get an estimate
We work on everything including:

-Electronic component upgrades
-Wheel building
-Bike packing and shipping 
-Bearing adjustments
-Shimano/SRAM brake bleeds
-Post-crash check overs
-Steel frame facing/chasing
-Etc.
